# Fuzzy Find

fzf <cmd>   # String search

#   Ctrl-t              search & review files  (multi-select with tab)
#   Ctrl-r              search & review history 
#   Alt-c               search & review folders tree (enter to cd into the folder)

#   '<string>           Strict search for <string> (no fuzzy search)

#   ^<string>           search files starting with <string> (Ex: ^.zsh)

#   <string>$           search file ending with <string> (Ex: json$)

#   tab                 select file 
#   shft-tab            deselect file

#   cd ** + Tab         only show directories 
#   export ** + Tab     only show env variables
#   unset ** + Tab      only show env variables to unset
#   ssh ** + Tab        only show past ssh hosts 
#   ps ** + Tab         only show processes
#   kill ** + Tab       only show processes
#   unalias ** + Tab    only show aliases



